PyGrip
------
Date: March 20th, 2013
Author: Justin Karneges <justin@fanout.io>

GRIP library for Python.

Sample usage:

  import grip

  http_body = grip.create_hold_response("mychannel")
  # django: HttpResponse(http_body, content_type="application/grip-instruct")

  grip.set_control_uri("https://api.fanout.io/realm/myrealm")
  grip.set_realm("myrealm")
  grip.set_secret("secret")

  grip.publish_http_response("mychannel", "stuff\n")
